text: Aage Holm (16 February 1890 - 4 October 1957) was a Danish swimmer. He competed in the men's 400 metre freestyle event at the 1908 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1890 births Category:1957 deaths Category:Danish male swimmers Category:Olympic swimmers of Denmark Category:Swimmers at the 1908 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Copenhagen
